thread.title: Don Henriks
thread.title_full: Solar Quotes reviewed by Don Henriks

author: Don Henriks
title: Don Henriks
text:
All three recommended companies responded to my request, but could only give a solid Quote: on physical inspection of the premises, which is all that could be expected of any genuine company.
I found that Finn and the group were good people to deal with and have no hesitation in recommending them to anyone interested in having solar installed.
Don Henriks
